messages.messageBody:
Wayne:

We had a long discussion about this a few months or so
ago. I'll see if I can look it up in the archives and
send it to you. The short answer is that there were no
"ranks" in a samurai army, not like in a modern army.
When I find the posts, I'll direct you to them and
they will explain further.

Nate
